cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks related to human parsing, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces novel techniques for feature and label adaptation, which are related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. Additionally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on different datasets, including surveillance videos and movies, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer security (cs.CR), respectively.
